title: 126 - Bullet To The Weenus
description: On today's show, the boys find out a HUGE secret that Mett has been hiding since he started working at PMI. They discuss the fine craftsmanship of the Amish, if they use iPhone apps or 3rd party apps, the new Spider-Man movie's small secrets, and much more in a jam-packed Pod-Fod. Nick sends you out with a list of BANGERZ. As always, send your submissions into @ThePodPMI on Twitter and Instagram to be featured on the show. We appreciate the hell out of you all for listening We'll see you on Wednesday.
